:class Alisia : #.KonductaHandler
    :field private  shared    CR‚Üź‚éēUCS 13
    :field private  shared    LF‚Üź‚éēUCS 10
    :field private shared      CRLF‚Üź‚éēUCS 13 10
    :field private shared      styles‚Üź‚ć¨
    :field public shared devCmds‚Üź'DETRAP' 'RETRAP'

        ‚ąá r‚ÜźGetStyles;home
            :Access public
      ‚ćĚ Lazy-load level styles from Config/alisia_styles.json5 (cached in shared field)
      :If 0=‚ČĘstyles
            styles‚Üź(‚éēJSON‚ć†'Dialect' 'JSON5')‚äÉ‚éēNGET(#.Home,'Config/alisia_styles.json5')
      :EndIf
      r‚Üźstyles
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźGetCommand subj        ‚ćĚ remove possible redirection from subject line
      :Access public
      r‚ÜźRMB(¬Į1+(subj‚ąä'> ')‚ć≥1)‚ÜĎsubj
