      :If 0<‚ČĘpurl‚ÜźPrivacyURL
          plain‚Üźplain,‚ćô'privacy_link_plain'purl
          html‚Üźhtml,‚ćô'privacy_link_html'purl
      :EndIf
     
      plain‚Üź‚ąäplain,‚äā‚éēUCS 10
      html‚Üź‚ąähtml,‚äā‚éēUCS 10
      ('In-Reply-To'Mid)SendMail replyTo('[',CFG.handler_cfg.list_name,']',‚ćô'helptit')plain html
    ‚ąá


    ‚ąá DevAction E;t;cmd1;mid;prefix;replyTo;StartOfLog
      :Access public
      prefix‚Üź'[',cfg.list_name,'] '
      mid‚ÜźE.headers{‚äÉ((‚ÜĎ‚ćļ)‚ć™‚äā'')[(‚ÜĎ‚ćļ)[;1]‚ć≥‚äā‚ćĶ;2]}'Message-ID'
      replyTo‚ÜźE.sender
      t‚Üź' '(‚Č†‚äÜ‚äĘ)E.subject
