    ‚ąá failed‚ÜźExtractBounceAddress E;headers;hv;matches
      ‚ćĚ Extracts the failed recipient address from an NDR/bounce email.
      ‚ćĚ 1. X-Failed-Recipients Header
      failed‚Üź''
      headers‚Üź‚ÜĎE.headers
      hv‚Üź‚äÉ(headers‚ć™‚äā'')[(headers[;1]‚ć≥‚äā'X-Failed-Recipients');2]
      :If 0<‚ČĘhv~' '
          failed‚Üź‚éēC,hv~' '
          ‚Üí0
      :EndIf
      ‚ćĚ 2. Final-Recipient: rfc822; addr  (RFC 3464 / message/delivery-status)
      matches‚Üź('Final-Recipient:\s*rfc822;\s*([a-zA-Z0-9_.+%-]+@[a-zA-Z0-9.-]+)'‚éēS'\1'‚ć†'IC' 1)E.Text
      :If 0<‚ČĘmatches
