    ‚ąá RecordBounce E;failed;sub;i;z;file;adm
      :Access public
      ‚ćĚ Process NDR: increment bounce counter, disable at threshold (3) + notify admins.
      failed‚ÜźExtractBounceAddress E
      :If 0=‚ČĘfailed
          'WARN' 'BOUNCE'Log'Bounce without recognizable recipient address'
          ‚Üí0
      :EndIf
      ‚ćĚ Do not count temporary errors (4.x.x) ‚ÄĒ only permanent failures (5.x.x) are real bounces
      :If (0<‚ČĘ('Status:\s*4\.\d'‚éēS'\0')E.Text)‚ąß0=‚ČĘ('Status:\s*5\.\d'‚éēS'\0')E.Text
          'INFO' 'BOUNCE'Log'Temporary error (4.x.x), bounce not counted'(‚äÜfailed)
          ‚Üí0
      :EndIf
      sub‚ÜźGetSubscribers 2
      i‚Üźsub.email‚ć≥‚ć•‚éēC‚äāfailed
      :If i>‚ČĘsub
          'WARN' 'BOUNCE'Log'Bounce for unknown address'(‚äÜfailed)
          ‚Üí0
      :EndIf
      z‚Üźi‚äÉsub
      z.bounces‚Üź{2=‚ćĶ.‚éēNC'bounces':‚ćĶ.bounces+1 ‚čĄ 1}z
      z.last_bounce‚Üź1 ‚éēDT‚äā‚éēTS
      sub[i]‚Üź‚äāz
      file‚ÜźCFG.config.Folder,'subscribers.json'
      (‚äā(‚éēJSON‚ć†'Compact' 0)sub)‚éēNPUT file 1
      'INFO' 'BOUNCE'Log('bounce #',(‚ćēz.bounces))(‚äÜfailed)
      :If z.bounces‚Č•3
          z.disabled‚Üź1
          sub[i]‚Üź‚äāz
          (‚äā(‚éēJSON‚ć†'Compact' 0)sub)‚éēNPUT file 1
          'WARN' 'BOUNCE'Log('disabled after ',(‚ćēz.bounces),' bounces')(‚äÜz.email)
          :For adm :In ,‚äÜcfg.admin_accounts
              SendMail adm(‚ćô'bounce_admin_tit'failed)(‚ćô'bounce_admin_body'failed(‚ćēz.bounces))
          :EndFor
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá ResetBounce sender;sub;i;s;addr
      ‚ćĚ Reset a subscriber's bounce counter when they actively communicate with the list.
      ‚ćĚ Proof of reachability: subscriber sends a mail or a command.
      ‚ćĚ Only reset if 0 < bounces < threshold (3) ‚ÄĒ do not touch disabled addresses.
      addr‚Üź#.getMaddr sender
      sub‚ÜźGetSubscribers 2
      i‚Üźsub.email‚ć≥‚ć•‚éēC‚äāaddr
      :If i>‚ČĘsub ‚čĄ ‚Üí0 ‚čĄ :EndIf  ‚ćĚ Subscriber not found
      s‚Üźi‚äÉsub
      :If s{6::0 ‚čĄ (0<‚ćļ‚ćé‚ćĶ)‚ąß3>‚ćļ‚ćé‚ćĶ}'bounces'
          s.bounces‚Üź0
          sub[i]‚Üź‚äās
          (‚äā(‚éēJSON‚ć†'Compact' 0)sub)‚éēNPUT(CFG.config.Folder,'subscribers.json')1
          'INFO' 'BOUNCE'Log'Bounce counter reset (active communication)'(‚äÜaddr)
      :EndIf
