    ‚ąá ok‚ÜźCheckRateLimit sender;file;data;now;ts;i;e;window;limit
      ‚ćĚ Rate-limiting: prevents abuse through too many commands in a short time.
      ‚ćĚ Configuration per list in triggers.json5 ‚Üí handler_cfg:
      ‚ćĚ   ratelimit_window_secs  Time window in seconds (default: 300 = 5 min.)
      ‚ćĚ   ratelimit_max          Max. commands per window (default: 10)
      ‚ćĚ Storage: CFG.config.Folder/ratelimit.json  (array of {email, ts})
      window‚Üź{2=‚ćĶ.‚éēNC'ratelimit_window_secs':‚ćĶ.ratelimit_window_secs ‚čĄ 300}cfg
      limit‚Üź{2=‚ćĶ.‚éēNC'ratelimit_max':‚ćĶ.ratelimit_max ‚čĄ 10}cfg
      file‚ÜźCFG.config.Folder,'ratelimit.json'
      data‚Üź{‚éēNEXISTS ‚ćĶ:(‚éēJSON‚ć†'Dialect' 'JSON5')1‚äÉ‚éēNGET ‚ćĶ ‚čĄ ‚ć¨}file
      now‚Üź20 ‚éēDT‚äā‚éēTS  ‚ćĚ Unix timestamp (seconds since 1970-01-01)
      :If 0=‚ČĘdata
          i‚Üź1  ‚ćĚ no entry yet ‚Üí "not found"
          ts‚Üź‚ć¨
      :Else
          i‚Üź(‚éēC¬®data.email)‚ć≥‚äā‚éēC sender
          ts‚Üź{‚ćĶ‚Č§‚ČĘdata:(‚ćĶ‚äÉdata).ts ‚čĄ ‚ć¨}i
      :EndIf
      ts‚Üź(ts‚Č•now-window)/ts  ‚ćĚ keep only timestamps within the window
      ok‚Üźlimit>‚ČĘts            ‚ćĚ 1=OK, 0=limit exceeded
      ts,‚Üźnow                 ‚ćĚ add current timestamp
      ‚ćĚ Update existing entry or create new one
      :If i‚Č§‚ČĘdata
          (i‚äÉdata).ts‚Üźts
      :Else
          e‚Üź‚éēNS''
          e.email‚Üź‚éēC sender
          e.ts‚Üźts
          data,‚Üź‚äāe
      :EndIf
      data‚Üź({0<‚ČĘ‚ćĶ.ts}¬®data)/data  ‚ćĚ clean up entries without recent timestamps
      (‚äā(‚éēJSON‚ć†'Compact' 0)data)‚éēNPUT file 1
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá res_ns‚ÜźSendAndAdd2Digest E;t;p;sub;e;c;s;msg;nam;smtp_cfg;Subject;res;hd;headers;file;orig_from;mmsg;email;ht;hb;tt;tb;b;smtp;txt;orig;data_folder;data;rx;part;‚éēTRAP;ti;chunk;multipart;i;attachments;iter;multiparts;‚ąÜ;len;h;y;htmlPart;textPart;inlineImages;inlineImagesNoCid;pt;alternative;cleanText;related;img;keptAttachments;mixed;blacklist;‚éēTRAP;opts
      :Access public
      blacklist‚ÜźGetBlacklist
     
      res_ns‚Üź‚éēNC''
      p‚Üź‚éēNPARTS E.Filename
      1 ‚éēMKDIR data_folder‚Üź(1‚äÉ‚éēNPARTS ¬Į1‚Üď1‚äÉp),'archive/'
      t‚Üźdata_folder,‚ąä1‚Üďp
      sub‚ÜźGetSubscribers 3 ‚ćĚ get subscribers
      ResetBounce E.sender  ‚ćĚ active list participation ‚Üí reset bounce counter if < threshold
      :If ‚éēNEXISTS file‚Üźdata_folder,'data.json5'
          data‚Üź(‚éēJSON‚ć†'Dialect' 'JSON5')1‚äÉ(‚éēNGET)file
      :Else
          data‚Üź‚éēNS'' ‚čĄ data.count‚Üź0
      :EndIf
      c‚Üźdata.count+1
      data.count‚Üźc
      (‚äā(‚éēJSON‚ć†'Compact' 0)data)‚éēNPUT(data_folder,'data.json5')1
      (p‚Üźdata_folder,(‚ćēc),'.eml')‚éēNCOPY E.Filename
      'INFO' 'SYS'Log'msg #',(‚ćēc),': "',E.subject,'" ‚Üí ',p
      e‚ÜźE.‚éēNS'subject' 'date' 'ticks'
     
      msg‚Üź‚éēNS''
      mmsg‚Üź‚éēNEW MimeMessage
      email‚Üźmmsg.Load p CancellationToken
     
      ti‚ÜźE.subject   ‚ćĚ from our json file
      rx‚Üź‚ćô'mailPrefix_tit'(cfg.name_short)'\d*'
      rx‚Üź('['‚éēR'\['‚ć†'Regex' 0)rx
      :While ‚ąÜ‚ČĘti‚Üź(rx ‚éēR''‚ć†'IC' 1)‚ąÜ‚Üźti
